	<item>
		<title>Behind the Lens: Editorial Shoot for Luxe Magazine</title>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>Our latest editorial shoot for Luxe Magazine took us to the Scottish Highlands. The brief was ambitious: capture the raw beauty of the landscape while showcasing the season's most opulent fashion.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>We spent five days traversing the Highlands, shooting at golden hour and working with natural light. The resulting series blends documentary realism with editorial flair.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Behind the scenes of our Scottish Highlands editorial shoot for Luxe Magazine — blending documentary realism with editorial flair.]]></excerpt:encoded>
