	<item>
		<title>Rebranding a Heritage Brand for the Digital Age</title>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>When a century-old luxury watchmaker approached us for a rebrand, we knew the challenge was to honor heritage while embracing modernity. The solution: a visual system that bridges the brand's storied past with a forward-looking digital presence.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>The new identity features a refined logotype, a custom typeface inspired by vintage watch dials, and a color palette drawn from aged brass and midnight blue.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[How we rebranded a century-old luxury watchmaker — honoring heritage while embracing a forward-looking digital presence.]]></excerpt:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>post</wp:post_type>
		<wp:post_name>heritage-brand-rebrand</wp:post_name>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
