		<category domain="category" nicename="branding"><![CDATA[Branding]]></category>
		<category domain="category" nicename="design"><![CDATA[Design]]></category>
	</item>

	<item>
		<title>Designing for Impact: Our Creative Process</title>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>Every project at Opulentia Studio follows a deliberate creative process. We start with deep research, move through iterative exploration, and arrive at solutions that are both beautiful and purposeful.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

		<!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"style":{"color":{"text":"#c9a96e"}}} -->
		<h3 class="wp-block-heading" style="color:#c9a96e">Phase 1: Discovery</h3>
		<!-- /wp:heading -->

		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>We immerse ourselves in the client's world — their audience, competitors, and aspirations.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[A look inside Opulentia Studio's creative process — from deep research to purposeful, beautiful solutions.]]></excerpt:encoded>
